# Feature layer

- Screens: `XxxScreen.kt` — stateless, collect `StateFlow`, handle `Event` in `LaunchedEffect`.
- ViewModels: no `android.*` imports; use `AppDependencies.shared`.
- Do not call `RankingRepository` directly — use domain use cases.
- Animations: prefer `QuizMotion` and theme tokens from `core:ui`.
